  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support 5 Rescued Horses Who Help People in Need</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Five horses rescued from neglect. Now with a new purpose in life, supporting our clients through equine-assisted programs at HOH/CDE in NW Puerto Rico. Over the last 2 years, our horses have empowered 50+ people, who have very limited access to services - including veterans/military and those with disabilities. They help people increase their confidence, social/communication skills, physical and mental abilities. This project funds their quality care and ongoing training to continue this work.</narrative>
  </description>
